data.description: LISTED BELOW ASSESSED VALUE! MOTIVATED SELLER! MOVE-IN READY 4 bedroom home in the heart of Harlingen. This property is located just minutes from the Expressway, Schools, Shopping outlets, brand new restaurants and Tesla chargers in the Stuart Place Plaza. This house is attractive both inside and out! It has a lovely open concept floor plan, the grand kitchen is a major eye catcher. It boasts dark stained cabinets, granite countertops, plenty of open space and a breakfast bar. The large living room and dining area make this home an easy place to entertain your friends and family. Master bedroom can hold large furniture, the master bath has double vanity, tiled shower and a large walk-in closet. The three spare bedrooms are all carpeted, and located central to your second bathroom. HVAC and thermostat were just serviced last month! House features a spacious indoor laundry room, huge privacy fenced backyard and even a well kept storage shed that conveys with this exceptional property!
